### Enable Focus Management with useFocusManager

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

Shows how to enable focus management for all components using the useFocusManager hook. Call enableFocus() to activate focus management, which is enabled by default. Useful when focus management has been previously disabled.

```javascript
import {useFocusManager} from 'ink';

const Example = () => {
	const {enableFocus} = useFocusManager();

	useEffect(() => {
		enableFocus();
	}, []);

	return …
};
```

