### Navigate to Next Focusable Component

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

Shows how to programmatically switch focus to the next focusable component using focusNext(). If no component is currently focused, focus goes to the first focusable component. Wraps around from last to first component.

```javascript
import {useFocusManager} from 'ink';

const Example = () => {
	const {focusNext} = useFocusManager();

	useEffect(() => {
		focusNext();
	}, []);

	return …
};
```

