### Enable raw mode for keyboard input handling in Ink

Source: https://github.com/vadimdemedes/ink/blob/master/readme.md

The setRawMode function from useStdin enables raw input mode to capture individual key presses including Ctrl+C. Must check isRawModeSupported before calling. This example shows proper setup and cleanup using useEffect to disable raw mode on unmount.

```javascript
import {useStdin} from 'ink';

const Example = () => {
	const {setRawMode} = useStdin();

	useEffect(() => {
		setRawMode(true);

		return () => {
			setRawMode(false);
		};
	});

	return …
};
```

